《'''Burn Out'''》是荷兰[[唱片骑师|DJ]][[马丁·盖瑞斯|马丁·盖瑞斯]]和{{tsl|en|Justin Mylo|贾斯汀·迈洛}}主唱，{{tsl|en|Dewain Whitmore Jr.|小德温·惠特摩尔|德温·惠特摩尔}}伴唱的单曲。歌曲于2018年9月14日通过盖瑞斯位于荷兰的唱片公司[[戳印唱片|戳印唱片]]发行，并独家授权给[[索尼音乐|索尼音乐]]旗下的[[史诗唱片|史诗阿姆斯特丹]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-drops-new-track-burn-out-listen |title=Martin Garrix drops new track, ‘Burn Out’ |publisher=[[DJ_Mag|DJ Mag]] |date= |accessdate=2018-09-16 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913220313/https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-drops-new-track-burn-out-listen |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
《Burn Out》是盖瑞斯与迈洛的第二首合作作品，此前他们曾共同演唱过《[[Bouncybob|Bouncybob]]》。2017年3月，歌曲在[[迈阿密|迈阿密]][[超世代音乐节|超世代音乐节]]上首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.garrixers.com/en_singleburnout.html|title=Burn Out - garrixers.com - Martin Garrix|work=Garrixers|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918115108/http://www.garrixers.com/en_singleburnout.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这首单曲在盖瑞斯和{{tsl|en|Axe (brand)|Axe}}合作推出新平台后正式发行。盖瑞斯说：“我很荣幸参加AXE音乐平台的发布活动。我喜欢AXE，当在工作室会面时，我们一见如故，这对我们的合作非常重要。我对新单曲《Burn Out》的视频非常满意<ref>{{cite web |author=Meadow, Matthew |url=https://www.youredm.com/2018/09/14/martin-garrix-announces-axe-partnership-with-release-of-justin-mylo-collab-burn-out/ |date=2018-09-14 |title=Martin Garrix Announces AXE Partnership With Release Of Justin Mylo Collab, "Burn Out" |publisher=Your EDM |accessdate=2018-09-16 |archive-date=2018-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916164410/https://www.youredm.com/2018/09/14/martin-garrix-announces-axe-partnership-with-release-of-justin-mylo-collab-burn-out/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://djtimes.com/martin-garrix-unites-justin-for-burn-out/ |title=Martin Garrix Unites With Justin Mylo For "Burn Out" |publisher=DJ Times |date= |accessdate=2018-09-16 |archive-date=2018-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916164359/https://djtimes.com/martin-garrix-unites-justin-for-burn-out/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==音乐视频==
《Burn Out》音乐视频同歌曲于2018年9月14日在[[Youtube|Youtube]]发行，总时长3分37秒<ref name=YouTube>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DylzGXE_ibU|title=Martin Garrix & Justin Mylo - Burn Out (Official Video) feat. Dewain Whitmore|work=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2018-09-14|accessdate=2020-09-18|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606173606/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DylzGXE_ibU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在视频中，男主人公在洗衣房里遇到了一位女孩并爱上了她，他们进入了不同的[[门户网站|门户网站]]，网站的主题与“他内心中的狂野现实”相似，最终男主人公获得了与她交谈的信心<ref name=billboard>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8475229/martin-garrix-justin-mylo-burn-out |title=Martin Garrix and Justin Mylo Team Up For Bubbly New Track 'Burn Out': Watch |publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date= |accessdate=2018-09-16 |archive-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914232334/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8475229/martin-garrix-justin-mylo-burn-out |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="weraveyou1"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/09/martin-garrix-justin-mylo-embody-sound-summer/ |title=Martin Garrix and Justin Mylo's chase a chart upstart with new single 'Burn Out' and accompanying music video |publisher={{tsl|en|Dancing Astronaut||Dancing Astronaut}} |date=2018-08-16 |accessdate=2018-09-16 |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915212456/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/09/martin-garrix-justin-mylo-embody-sound-summer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。马丁·盖瑞斯在视频开头短暂露面<ref name=YouTube />。

==评价==
《[[公告牌|公告牌]]》称《Burn Out》为“有趣而轻快的夏末果酱，流行舞蹈令人振奋并带有时髦的合成线。”同时称这首歌“足够盛大”以出现在音乐节中，并且“足够可爱”以作为与朋友在长时间开车时一起聆听的音乐<ref name=billboard />。

